1. *Prošli* mjesec uštedjeli smo puno novca. (Last month we saved a lot of money.)
2. Naša *prošla* škola bila je puno bolja. (Our last school was much better.)
3. *Prošle* godine ponovo smo se sreli. (We met again last year.)
4. On je bio glavni akter *prošlog* filma. (He was the main character of the last movie.)
5. *Prošlo* ljeto bilo je veoma vruće. (Last summer was very hot.)